snippet: Seattle forward Clint Dempsey was left off the United States roster for its opening qualifiers for the 2018 World Cup.
abstract: United States national soccer team leaves former captain Clint Dempsey off its roster for 2018 World Cup opening qualifiers and adds Darlington Nagbe and Matt Miazga, who could make their national team debuts; other soccer news noted.
